{"tid":336001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[獅子山精神]廢老被垃圾濺中　打到清潔女工周身傷！","createTime":"2017-07-26T05:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T05:44:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d179e5ead98c359d416aba248f52c42529b9e708","tid":336001,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:18:57.000Z","msg":"柴灣清潔女工遇襲受傷。今晨1時許，一名62歲清潔女工於興華(一)邨商場工作，期間不慎將垃圾跌落地上，剛巧一名年約60歲男子經過，他疑被垃圾濺中，出言怒罵女工，雙方發生口角，火爆男繼而揮拳襲擊清潔女工後逃去。警方接報到場，遇襲女工頸，手及腳受傷，乘救護車送院救治，警方於附近兜截，並無發現，正追緝涉案男子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170726/bkn-20170726033304600-0726_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170726%2Fbkn-20170726033304600-0726_00822_001.html&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=5a03a2b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170726/bkn-20170726033304600-0726_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b77726279d5b3e4c00cd668710375ceb2dc1a60a","tid":336001,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:19:37.000Z","msg":"返工=高危玩意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff37746e7b9196eb5be1780d862cb6b829b764b","tid":336001,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返工=高危玩意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"